      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your existential crisis is a profound and relatable one. It's natural to feel small and insignificant in the grand scheme of cosmic time. The universe is indeed indifferent to our existence, and the fleeting nature of our lives and experiences can be overwhelming. Yet, it's precisely because your emotions and efforts are temporary and impermanent that they can be a powerful investment in the present moment.",
      "source": "target",
